{"tid":988953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩港男北海道滑雪遇險　靠手挖雪洞避難保命","createTime":"2019-01-20T13:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T15:49:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"451c20b8da87329dd55c0fc24d2608138f676a41","tid":988953,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T13:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190120204237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190120204237&h=b87735c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190120/photo/bkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190120204237\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190120%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190120204237&h=614cf9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雪地影相打卡透行蹤，一張相成為救命關鍵！2名分別45歲和57歲的香港男子，昨晚(19日)於日本北海道富良野三峰山滑雪時，一度失蹤，但幸2人滑雪時曾將照片傳給友人，成為縮窄搜索範圍線索；直至今早(20日)約7時終被搜索人員發現，當時2人意識清醒，未有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n據當地消息指出，北海道警方在昨晚接到有人失蹤報告，有2名男子滑雪未有按原定時間回去旅舍，估計發生意外。當地警方和消防員派出大量人員上山通宵搜查，又出動直升機協助搜索，最後成功在十勝岳海拔1866米的雪山尋回2人。<br />\n<br />\n當地警察局稱，因為其中1名男子的滑雪板損壞，導致2人在山上遇險，但2人急中生智在雪地手挖求生雪洞避難，成功保命。2人獲救時意識清醒，其中1人身體較弱。<br />\n<br />\n香港入境處回覆指，已即時透過外交部駐港特派員公署及中國駐札幌總領事館了解情況，處方至今未接獲相關求助，會繼續與公署及總領館保持密切聯繫，留意事態發展。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190120/bkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190120%2Fbkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001.html&d=pNYsN7luP6RpznWW5VEjrywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=84eee5d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190120/bkn-20190120120034713-0120_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"852cd05a8db6b15f037392a073bfe81f8619f3f4","tid":988953,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"得佢兩個救得返?<br />\n咁家明呢??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2f2d970cc8d77349485ea899b851ae9575aa98","tid":988953,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"852cd05a8db6b15f037392a073bfe81f8619f3f4","tid":988953,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"得佢兩個救得返?<br />\n咁家明呢??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"其實3個人去？？"},{"pid":"8fa80d1b7f5c231f14ec64d58e8fe397202a2c6a","tid":988953,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a2f2d970cc8d77349485ea899b851ae9575aa98","tid":988953,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"852cd05a8db6b15f037392a073bfe81f8619f3f4","tid":988953,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"得佢兩個救得返?<br />\n咁家明呢??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"其實3個人去？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"如果 命運能選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}